 from ₹400 per night, with options across 7 price categories."},{"q":"What are the top places to visit in McLeod Ganj?","a":"The top attractions are Tsuglagkhang Complex, Triund Trek, Bhagsu Waterfall, Dal Lake Dharamsala, Namgyal Monastery."}],"seo":{"title":"McLeod Ganj Travel Guide 2026 — Places, Hotels, How to Reach | IndiaExplore","description":"Tibetan culture, Dalai Lama's residence, Triund Trek and the dramatic Dhauladhar range. Plan your McLeod Ganj trip: 13 places to visit, 11 stays from ₹400/night, best time (Mar – Jun, Sep – Nov) and routes.","canonical":"destination.html?slug=mcleodganj","ogImage":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Interior_of_Main_Monks%27_Hall_-_Tsuglagkhang_Complex_-_McLeod_Ganj_-_Himachal_Pradesh_-_India_%2826171197073%29.jpg/1280px-Interior_of_Main_Monks%27_Hall_-_Tsuglagkhang_Complex_-_McLeod_Ganj_-_Himachal_Pradesh_-_India_%2826171197073%29.jpg","keywords":["McLeod Ganj travel guide","places to visit in McLeod Ganj","McLeod Ganj hotels","best time to visit McLeod Ganj","how to reach McLeod Ganj","Himachal Pradesh tourism"]}}